description:
Do you want to learn how to design simple user interface for web, app or mobile and make some extra money? Or you just like to improve your designing skills in Photoshop? This course is the best course for you.

This course is designed to teach you about GUI or graphic use interface and how to earn extra money from doing this. In this course you will learn not only about doing designs but also how to make a career as freelance designer. I will teach you how to maximize your talent and build your confidence.

  • You Can Use either Mac or Windows
  • No Prior Experience
  • No coding or Programming
  • Design User Interface From Scratch in Photoshop
  • Basic Photoshop knowledge
If you are ready to learn then enroll now and see you inside.
title: Designing GUI kits in Photoshop for beginners
